# cat experience: type command, show output, clear, repeat
Output assets/experience.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 420
Set Height 320
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show

Type "cat experience"
Enter
Sleep 4s
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 600ms

Type "cat experience"
Enter
Sleep 4s
